data.description: Come see this beautifully remodeled home in Ponder while you can.  The kitchen and baths have all new cabinets and tile, new granite in the kitchen along with new appliances.  Fresh paint inside and out, all new carpet on the second story, and the roof was replaced 3 months ago.  This home is ready for you to move in and make it your own, nestled in quiet little community in the country with a large neighborhood park and no hassle of HOA restrictions on this home.  Come see this wonderful home today!
